race.comment: SYNCOPATED SHUFFLE (7) produced another strong performance last time when she battled on bravely to finish second over 2170m at this track. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. Good enough to put herself back in the winners' stall. ROCK WHAT YOU ARE (1) finished seventh last start at this track over 2170m. Capable of playing a major role so has to be respected. MOVINTOHELLANDBACK (8) is on the radar after her last-start sixth over 2170m at this track a week ago. ANGELIC ATTITUDE (5) followed a solid third first-up two runs back with a distant retired when she was interfered with and broke in a 2170m event at this track. Meets a similar lineup so if she has some luck, a big run is likely.
